* Desmonus simply flew out of the range of Deemons shot, watching it as it 
simply saied off in the distance.
But when she turned her head back towards the bot something else caught her 
eyes...it was some sort of giant bot!
She looked at it but in her mind she knew what it was anyway, her new 
programming giving her all the info she needed. It was Oblitertron.
But she was hardely impressed by the huge bot that began to run after some 
maximal...or something like that. But then most of the Alliance were going 
after him as well, following the great monster of a machine at full speed.
She sighed, looking down and seeing nothing much worth of interest. Simply 
turning towards the figure of Oblitertron and flying after him as well.
She was still farely new at this, but she would get the hang of it sooner or 
later...when she fed and her energy was up.
The bladed boomerang returned to her hand as she flew, the replacing it in 
her back compatrment.
Still, wings beating quickly, she followed the rest to see what they were up 
to.*
